I can't even start to explain how much i'm hooked on this show,i absolutely LOVE it! Great storyline,great flow of the story,a lot of twists,fantastic actors and actresses and great production. Love the whole idea.If you like:drama,criminal conspiracies,love stories,family feuds and comedic moments,this is the perfect show for you. You'll find yourself crying at one point,laughing at another.I can't exclude how AMAZING the music is,every song is perfect for an according moment,either sad,blow-up things in the air moments,happy moments,moments of regret,you name it.Overall,i love,love absolutely LOVEE this series and i place SOA in my top 5,being my #1! My personal favorite characters are Jax,Gemma,Juice and Tig. Watch it,you won't regret it!